{{!< default}}

{{!-- ===== HERO ===== --}}
<section class="hero bg-pattern">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-content">
        {{#match @site.locale "=" "en"}}
          <h1>Get Your Time Back</h1>
          <p class="hero-subtitle">We build automated workflows that cut admin, reduce errors, and free your team to focus on real work.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="{{@site.url}}/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Discovery Call <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg></a>
            <a href="{{@site.url}}/services/" class="btn btn-secondary">See What We Automate</a>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-trust">
            <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><polyline points="9 12 11 14 15 10"/></svg>
            <span>Quebec grants can cover up to 50% of your project. We help you apply.</span>
          </div>
        {{else}}
          <h1>Reprenez le contrôle de votre temps</h1>
          <p class="hero-subtitle">On met en place des workflows automatisés qui réduisent l'admin, limitent les erreurs et redonnent du temps à votre équipe.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="{{@site.url}}/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Réserver un appel découverte <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg></a>
            <a href="{{@site.url}}/services/" class="btn btn-secondary">Voir ce qu'on automatise</a>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-trust">
            <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><polyline points="9 12 11 14 15 10"/></svg>
            <span>Les subventions québécoises peuvent couvrir jusqu'à 50% de votre projet. On s'occupe de la demande.</span>
          </div>
        {{/match}}
      </div>
      <div class="hero-illustration" aria-hidden="true">
        <img src="{{asset "images/hero-illustration.png"}}" alt="Workflow automation: from chaos to order" style="width:100%;max-width:480px;height:auto;border-radius:16px;">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{{!-- ===== PAIN POINTS ===== --}}
<section class="section pain-redesign wash-orange" id="problems">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="pain-redesign-grid">
      <div class="pain-redesign-intro">
        {{#match @site.locale "=" "en"}}
          <p class="section-label">Sound familiar?</p>
          <h2 class="pain-redesign-title">Your team is buried in follow-ups</h2>
        {{else}}
          <p class="section-label">Ça vous parle?</p>
          <h2 class="pain-redesign-title">Votre équipe se noie dans les suivis</h2>
        {{/match}}
      </div>
      <div class="pain-redesign-list" aria-label="Common business pain points">
        {{#match @site.locale "=" "en"}}
          <div class="pain-redesign-row">
            <span class="pain-redesign-index">01</span>
            <p>Quotes, reminders, approvals, status updates. The work keeps moving, but someone is always stuck pushing it along by hand.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-redesign-row">
            <span class="pain-redesign-index">02</span>
            <p>A missed email. A forgotten task. A client left waiting. Small gaps turn into delays, rework, and lost trust.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-redesign-row">
            <span class="pain-redesign-index">03</span>
            <p>Not because your people aren't good — because they're stuck doing repetitive, manual work that's beneath what you hired them for.</p>
          </div>
        {{else}}
          <div class="pain-redesign-row">
            <span class="pain-redesign-index">01</span>
            <p>Soumissions, rappels, approbations, mises à jour. Le travail avance, mais il faut toujours quelqu'un pour le faire suivre à la main.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-redesign-row">
            <span class="pain-redesign-index">02</span>
            <p>Un courriel oublié. Une tâche manquée. Un client qui attend. Les petits oublis deviennent des délais, du retravail et de la confiance perdue.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-redesign-row">
            <span class="pain-redesign-index">03</span>
            <p>Pas parce que vos gens ne sont pas bons — parce qu'ils sont pris à faire du travail répétitif et manuel qui est en dessous de ce pour quoi vous les avez engagés.</p>
          </div>
        {{/match}}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pain-redesign-closing">
      {{#match @site.locale "=" "en"}}
        <p>We fix the handoffs, the follow-ups, and the admin work so your team can focus on what actually matters.</p>
      {{else}}
        <p>On s'occupe des transferts, des suivis et de l'administratif pour que votre équipe se concentre sur ce qui compte vraiment.</p>
      {{/match}}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

